<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Elite Bridge - Professional Caregiver Staffing Platform</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            background: #f5f7fa;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* HEADER & NAVIGATION */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e5631 0%, #2d7a3e 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(30, 86, 49, 0.15);
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .mode-selector {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .mode-btn {
            padding: 12px 28px;
            font-size: 1em;
            border: 2px solid #1e5631;
            background: white;
            color: #1e5631;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .mode-btn.active {
            background: #1e5631;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(30, 86, 49, 0.2);
        }

        .mode-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(30, 86, 49, 0.2);
        }

        .content {
            display: none;
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
        }

        .content.active {
            display: block;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        /* SECTIONS */
        .section {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border-top: 4px solid #1e5631;
        }

        .section h2 {
            color: #1e5631;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e7ff;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .section h3 {
            color: #2d7a3e;
            margin-top: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.3em;
        }

        /* CLIENT PORTAL SPECIFIC */
        .client-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e5631 0%, #2d7a3e 50%, #0f3d1f 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(30, 86, 49, 0.2);
        }

        .client-hero h2 {
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 2em;
        }

        .client-hero p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            font-size: 1.05em;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .quick-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .quick-stat {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f8f5 0%, #e8f5e9 100%);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 5px solid #1e5631;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .quick-stat .number {
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e5631;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .quick-stat .label {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .care-request-form {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f8f5 0%, #e8f5e9 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 2px solid #1e5631;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #1e5631;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .form-group input,
        .form-group select,
        .form-group textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            font-family: inherit;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .form-group input:focus,
        .form-group select:focus,
        .form-group textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #1e5631;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(30, 86, 49, 0.1);
        }

        .form-group textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 120px;
        }

        .booking-card {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #e0e7f1;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .booking-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e5631 0%, #2d7a3e 100%);
        }

        .booking-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(30, 86, 49, 0.15);
            border-color: #1e5631;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .booking-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: start;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .booking-title {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e5631;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .booking-status {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .booking-status.active {
            background: #c8e6c9;
            color: #00695c;
        }

        .booking-status.completed {
            background: #b3e5fc;
            color: #01579b;
        }

        .booking-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .booking-detail {
            background: #f8fafb;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 3px solid #1e5631;
        }

        .booking-detail label {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .booking-detail value {
            color: #1e5631;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.05em;
        }

        .booking-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .booking-actions button {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 150px;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        .booking-actions .btn-primary {
            background: #1e5631;
            color: white;
        }

        .booking-actions .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #2d7a3e;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(30, 86, 49, 0.2);
        }

        .booking-actions .btn-secondary {
            background: #e8f5e9;
            color: #1e5631;
            border: 2px solid #1e5631;
        }

        .booking-actions .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #c8e6c9;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .caregiver-info {
            background: #f0f8f5;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #1e5631;
        }

        .caregiver-info strong {
            color: #1e5631;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .caregiver-info p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        /* GRID LAYOUTS */
        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: #f8fafb;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 5px solid #1e5631;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(30, 86, 49, 0.15);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .feature-card h4 {
            color: #1e5631;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .feature-card .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e0f2f1;
            color: #00695c;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* STATS */
        .stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .stat-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e5631 0%, #2d7a3e 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(30, 86, 49, 0.15);
        }

        .stat-box .number {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .stat-box .label {
            font-size: 0.95em;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* TABS */
        .tabs {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .tab-btn {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
            color: #666;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .tab-btn.active {
            color: #1e5631;
            border-bottom-color: #1e5631;
        }

        .tab-content {
            display: none;
        }

        .tab-content.active {
            display: block;
        }

        /* LIST ITEMS */
        .list-item {
            padding: 18px;
            background: #f8fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            border-left: 5px solid #1e5631;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .list-item:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(30, 86, 49, 0.1);
        }

        .list-item strong {
            color: #1e5631;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 1.05em;
        }

        .list-item p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        /* FORMS */
        .demo-section {
            background: #f0f8f5;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 2px solid #1e5631;
        }

        .demo-form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .demo-form input,
        .demo-form select,
        .demo-form textarea {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            font-family: inherit;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .demo-form input:focus,
        .demo-form select:focus,
        .demo-form textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #1e5631;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(30, 86, 49, 0.1);
        }

        .demo-form textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 120px;
        }

        .demo-form button {
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background: #1e5631;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1em;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            align-self: flex-start;
        }

        .demo-form button:hover {
            background: #2d7a3e;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(30, 86, 49, 0.2);
        }

        /* BUTTONS */
        button {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        button:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }

        .btn-primary {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: #1e5631;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #2d7a3e;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #e8f5e9;
            color: #1e5631;
            border: 1px solid #1e5631;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #c8e6c9;
        }

        .btn-danger {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #d32f2f;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        .btn-danger:hover {
            background: #c62828;
        }

        /* CAREGIVER CARD */
        .caregiver-card {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #e0e7f1;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .caregiver-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(30, 86, 49, 0.15);
            border-color: #1e5631;
        }

        .caregiver-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: start;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .caregiver-info h4 {
            color: #1e5631;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .caregiver-rating {
            color: #ffc107;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .caregiver-badges {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e8f5e9;
            color: #1e5631;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .badge.verified {
            background: #c8e6c9;
            color: #00695c;
        }

        /* MESSAGING */
        .message-container {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #e0e7f1;
            border-radius: 10px;
            height: 400px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .messages {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .message {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .message.sent {
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        .message-bubble {
            max-width: 70%;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .message.received .message-bubble {
            background: #f0f8f5;
            color: #333;
        }

        .message.sent .message-bubble {
            background: #1e5631;
            color: white;
        }

        .message-input {
            padding: 15px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e7f1;
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .message-input input {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .message-input button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #1e5631;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* FOOTER */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            color: #666;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .github-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: #333;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .github-link:hover {
            background: #555;
        }

        /* RESPONSIVE */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8em;
            }

            .mode-selector {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .mode-btn {
                width: 100%;
            }

            .feature-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .caregiver-header {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .message-bubble {
                max-width: 90%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>🏥 Elite Bridge</h1>
            <p>Professional Caregiver Staffing Platform</p>
        </header>

        <div class="mode-selector">
            <button class="mode-btn active" onclick="switchMode('client')">👨‍👩‍👧 Client Portal</button>
            <button class="mode-btn" onclick="switchMode('directory')">👥 Caregiver Directory</button>
            <button class="mode-btn" onclick="switchMode('staff')">👤 Staff Portal</button>
            <button class="mode-btn" onclick="switchMode('admin')">👨‍💼 Admin Dashboard</button>
            <button class="mode-btn" onclick="switchMode('messaging')">💬 Messaging</button>
        </div>

        <!-- CLIENT/FAMILY PORTAL -->
        <div id="client" class="content active">
            <div class="section">
                <h2>Request Care Services</h2>
                <p>Find trusted, verified caregivers for your loved ones. Submit your care needs and we'll match you with the perfect caregiver.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h3>📋 Submit Care Request</h3>
                <div class="demo-section">
                    <div class="demo-form">
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" value="Jane Smith">
                        <input type="email" placeholder="Email Address" value="jane@example.com">
                        <input type="tel" placeholder="Phone Number" value="(555) 123-4567">
                        
                        <select>
                            <option selected>Select Care Type</option>
                            <option>Companion Care</option>
                            <option>Personal Care</option>
                            <option>Household Support</option>
                            <option>Mobility Assistance</option>
                            <option>Medication Reminders</option>
                        </select>

                        <select>
                            <option selected>Frequency</option>
                            <option>One-time</option>
                            <option>Daily</option>
                            <option>Weekly</option>
                            <option>Monthly</option>
                        </select>

                        <input type="date" placeholder="Start Date">
                        
                        <textarea placeholder="Describe care needs and any special requirements..."></textarea>
                        
                        <button class="btn-primary" onclick="alert('Care request submitted! We\'ll match you with caregivers shortly.')">Submit Care Request</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h3>📊 My Care Bookings</h3>
                <div class="list-item">
                    <strong>Active: Companion Care - Mary Johnson</strong>
                    <p><strong>Schedule:</strong> Monday & Wednesday, 2:00 PM - 5:00 PM</p>
                    <p><strong>Rate:</strong> $22/hour | <strong>Status:</strong> ✅ Confirmed</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 10px; color: #666;">Next visit: Monday, June 17 at 2:00 PM</p>
                    <button class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top: 10px;">View Details</button>
                    <button class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">Message Caregiver</button>
                </div>
                <div class="list-item">
                    <strong>Completed: Personal Care - Robert Davis</strong>
                    <p><strong>Schedule:</strong> June 10-14, Daily 9:00 AM - 12:00 PM</p>
                    <p><strong>Rate:</strong> $25/hour | <strong>Status:</strong> ✅ Completed</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 10px; color: #666;">Total Hours: 15 | Total Cost: $375</p>
                    <button class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top: 10px;">Leave Review</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h3>💰 Billing & Payments</h3>
                <div class="stats">
                    <div class="stat-box">
                        <div class="number">$1,250</div>
                        <div class="label">Total Spent</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-box">
                        <div class="number">$375</div>
                        <div class="label">This Month</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-box">
                        <div class="number">12</div>
                        <div class="label">Care Sessions</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CAREGIVER DIRECTORY -->
        <div id="directory" class="content">
            <div class="section">
                <h2>Find Verified Caregivers</h2>
                <p>Browse our network of background-checked, certified caregivers. All profiles are verified for quality and safety.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h3>🔍 Search & Filter</h3>
                <div class="demo-section">
                    <div class="demo-form">
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Search by name or specialty...">
                        
                        <select>
                            <option selected>All Care Types</option>
                            <option>Companion Care</option>
                            <option>Personal Care</option>
                            <option>Household Support</option>
                            <option>Mobility Assistance</option>
                        </select>

                        <select>
                            <option selected>Minimum Rating</option>
                            <option>4.5+ Stars</option>
                            <option>4.0+ Stars</option>
                            <option>3.5+ Stars</option>
                            <option>All</option>
                        </select>

                        <button class="btn-primary" onclick="alert('Search results updated!')">Search Caregivers</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h3>👥 Featured Caregivers</h3>
                
                <div class="caregiver-card">
                    <div class="caregiver-header">
                        <div class="caregiver-info">
                            <h4>Mary Johnson</h4>
                            <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 8px;">Companion Care Specialist</p>
                            <div class="caregiver-rating">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 4.9/5 (47 reviews)</div>
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn-primary">Book Now</button>
                    </div>
